summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6278 for the improvement of 34th Ave. Southwest from Southwest Brandon St. to Southwest Juneau St.; and certain other streets, avenues and alleys; by sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 91898, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
